thread.title: Sally Payne
thread.title_full: Green Lake Jewelry reviewed by Sally Payne

author: Sally Payne
title: Sally Payne
text: It truly was a pleasure working with Sophia at Green Lake Jewelry in designing my beautiful ring. She did a great shop of taking my ideas making them a reality. All the work was done in the time frame as stated. I would not hesitate at all to recommend the store to anyone interested in custom jewelry. The quality and workmanship is outstanding.
